songs.title: Driving In Circles [Dancin’ In Circles Demo]
songs.lyrics:
Verse 1:
I lay around
Touch myself to pass the time
Role around
I wish you were mine
I close my eyes
Hold myself and I picture us
In a place I don't recognize

Pre-Chorus:
--- out of this cage
When I'm around you I just can't behave

Chorus:
Baby don't cry
Baby don't cry
I'm driving in circles
It's hard to be lonely
Baby don't cry
Baby don't cry
